import { toC, toMps, toDeg, toClock } from "../lib/format"; export default function WeatherCard({ data, onOpen }) { const tz = data?.timezone ?? 0; return (
onOpen?.(data)} style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}> {/* Top */}
{data?.name || "-"}
{data?.description || "-"}
{toC(data?.temp)}
Temp Min: {toC(data?.temp_min)}
Temp Max: {toC(data?.temp_max)}
{/* Meta */}
Pressure {data?.pressure != null ? `${data.pressure} hPa` : "-"}
Humidity {data?.humidity != null ? `${data.humidity}%` : "-"}
Visibility {data?.visibility != null ? `${(data.visibility / 1000).toFixed(1)} km` : "-"}
Wind {toMps(data?.wind_speed)}
Direction {toDeg(data?.wind_deg)}
Sunrise {toClock(data?.sunrise, tz)}
Sunset {toClock(data?.sunset, tz)}
); }
